LE3u1gXT9sQ7kNvgFXt48v&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBwFcPMLldFwKb2cO4WLK3C6cxRgikkBj2NeRk-G4FKIA&oe=67486A10"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "146428790027337", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974540_1006289679517978_5227941115902033920_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=UzA1m5lVK5MQ7kNvgHkFkva&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAs4ZeECFvubEXY2nMVuAhjPYn7Fcn9JLTZgsGbt4oxRw&oe=674849DC"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "VR Mini Bowling", "keywords": ["Bowling", "Golf", "Mini", "Sports", "VR"], "long_description": "Welcome to the world of Mini Bowling!  In this VR game bowling meets mini golf to create a totally new experience!\n\nKey Features:\n- 3 Scoring Modes\n- 3 courses with 10 unique lanes each\n- Traditional bowling lane with realistic physics (spin, oil patterns)!\n- 24 bowling balls to choose from (16 unlockable)\n- Customizable sound effects\n- Customizable pin colors\n- Anti-gravity pins\n- Throw force multiplier\n\nStandard Mode:\nIn this game mode, normal bowling rules apply.  Try to get the highest score possible!\n\nStroke Play Mode:\nThis mode will put your skills to the test! The goal is to knock down all of the pins in as few throws as possible.\n\nRush Play Mode:\nSpeed is the key in this mode.  Knock down all of the pins as quickly as possible!  You get unlimited throws in this mode so fire away!\n\nTraditional Mode:\nFeel like changing it up and playing a regular game of bowling? You can! Put spin on the ball to curve it down the lane, and even change the oil pattern on the lane!", "short_description": "Welcome to the world of Mini Bowling!  In this VR game bowling meets mini golf to create a totally new experience!"}]}, "developer_name": "Brian Macumber", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://mac13rosstudios.com/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Brian Macumber"